				\begin{document}$$ {\text{O}}_2^{-} $$\end{document} anions. By contrast, the holes possessing positive charge can interact with hydroxyl or water molecules to oxidize them into hydroxyl radicals. It is these radicals that act on the organic compounds by decomposing them [88].
